<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja" class="dark">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>BetValue Finder - 期待値自動判定システム</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400&family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Inter', 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif; }
        textarea, .font-mono { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 8px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: #1e293b; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #475569; border-radius: 4px; }
        .spinner {
            border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-top-color: #ffffff;
            animation: spin 1s linear infinite;
        }
        @keyframes spin { to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-900 text-slate-300">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-3xl p-4 sm:p-6">
        <header class="flex justify-between items-center py-4 mb-6">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="bg-sky-500/10 p-2 rounded-lg">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="text-sky-400">
                        <path d="m12 14 4-4"/><path d="M3.34 19a10 10 0 1 1 17.32 0"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h1 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-white">BetValue Finder</h1>
            </div>
        </header>
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-5 sm:p-6 space-y-6">
            <div>
                <label for="paste-input" class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-300 mb-2">ハンデを入力（競技は自動判定）</label>
                <textarea id="paste-input" class="w-full h-40 p-3 bg-slate-900 border border-slate-700 rounded-lg text-slate-200 placeholder-slate-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-sky-500 focus:border-sky-500 outline-none transition" placeholder="例：
ヤンキース<0.5>
レッドソックス

ドジャース
パドレス<1半>"></textarea>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-2">※ <>付きの側がフェイバリット</p>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                <div>
                    <label for="rakeback-select" class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-300 mb-2">レーキバック</label>
                    <select id="rakeback-select" class="w-full p-2.5 bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 rounded-lg">
                        <option value="0">0%</option>
                        <option value="0.015" selected>1.5%</option>
                        <option value="0.030">3.0%</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-300 mb-2">日本式配当</label>
                    <input type="text" value="1.90倍" disabled class="w-full p-2.5 bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 rounded-lg text-slate-400">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4">
                <button id="clear-btn" class="px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-slate-700 text-slate-200 font-semibold hover:bg-slate-600">クリア</button>
                <button id="analyze-btn" class="flex-1 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-sky-600 text-white font-semibold hover:bg-sky-500">判定する</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <section id="results-section" class="mt-8 hidden">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">判定結果</h2>
            <div id="results-container" class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4"></div>
        </section>
    </div>
    <script src="/static/app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
